        "content": "<p>The existence is in <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=exists_norm_eq_iInf_of_complete_convex#doc\">docs#exists_norm_eq_iInf_of_complete_convex</a>, the uniqueness is essentially the next lemma in this file.</p>",
